                <h1>“The Meaning Behind the Green Check Mark”</h1>
                <p>The green check mark symbolizes approval, completion, or correctness. Often used in digital interfaces, it signifies that a task is done or a choice is verified. Visually, it conveys positivity and trust, making it a favorite in design. Whether in apps or documents, the green check mark enhances user experience by indicating successful outcomes.</p>
